com.vmware.connectors.common.payloads.response

Class CardBodyField.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.connectors.common.payloads.response.CardBodyField.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    CardBodyField

    public static class CardBodyField.Builder
extends Object
    This class allows the construction of CardBodyField objects. To use, create a Builder instance, call its methods to populate the CardBodyField, and call build() to receive the completed CardBodyField and reset the builder.

    A CardBodyField can be discarded during creation, returning the Builder to its initial state, by calling reset(). The build() method calls reset() internally.
